name: The Sister I Never Had - 1
description:
You held my hand through the dark
You had my back through it all
You’re the sister I never had
We laughed under the sun
We danced under the rain
You’re the sister I never had
You never let me down, you always stayed around
You’ve always fought for me, but kept my feet firmly on the ground
You’re truly the sister I never had
But like everyone else had, life happened
We both grew quickly, like that little summer rain
You had your life and priorities, I had mine
We grew apart but you’ll always be the sister I never had.

by Jovierose
